350
00:27:12,130 --> 00:27:13,680
I'm going to see the doctor first.

351
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,410
Don't worry.

352
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,610
Your son, staying with me,

353
00:27:15,610 --> 00:27:16,730
