391
00:29:40,650 --> 00:29:41,450
Not only that.

392
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,300
What else?

393
00:29:45,050 --> 00:29:46,590
I helped you with the sweating.

394
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:47,850
I also wiped your body.

395
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,440
So, as we said before,

396
00:29:51,490 --> 00:29:52,840
marry me, deal?

397
00:29:55,340 --> 00:29:56,070
I don't care.

398
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:57,240
I'm going to tell my mum now

399
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:58,540
