She said she would bless us.

406
00:30:14,130 --> 00:30:14,660
Hurry up.

407
00:30:35,870 --> 00:30:38,330
I'll warm up a towel for you to wipe your face.

408
00:31:10,390 --> 00:31:11,180
Seriously.

409
00:31:12,230 --> 00:31:14,360
You've been lazy since you were young.

410
00:31:25,250 --> 00:31:26,380
Lie down for a while.

411
00:31:58,630 --> 00:31:59,460
Xu Yao?

412
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,060
Did anything happen?

413
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,940
It's okay. I'll call you when I get back.

414
00:32:19,380 --> 00:32:20,310
Are you jealous?

415
00:32:21,690 --> 00:32:23,220
You are not allowed to do so.

416
00:32:27,820 --> 00:32:28,880
What are you doing?

417
00:32:31,310 --> 00:32:31,910
Calm down.

418
00:32:32,130 --> 00:32:33,460
It's in broad daylight.

419
00:32:34,910 --> 00:32:36,390
I've been taking care of you all-day

420
00:32:36,390 --> 00:32:37,920
