421
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:41,720
Give me 20 minutes.

422
00:32:41,940 --> 00:32:43,000
We'll go out later.

423
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,020
Lu Chen.

424
00:33:02,210 --> 00:33:02,810
Why did you

425
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:04,350
leave Qining back then?

426
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,020
I mean,

427
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,380
