430
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,790
Is it hard to say?

431
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,880
Let me think about it.

432
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,660
I'll think about how to explain it to you.

433
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:28,310
Forget it. I don't want to know.

434
00:33:38,980 --> 00:33:40,980
The first two years I came to Qining,

435
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:43,390
I had three choices.

436
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,180
There were two leaders

437
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,240
who came from here.

438
00:33:46,930 --> 00:33:47,930
When recruiting,

439
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:49,500
the old captain

440
00:33:49,500 --> 00:33:51,030
talked to me for a few hours.

441
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:54,120
He knew I lived in Beijing,

442
00:33:55,250 --> 00:33:56,450
far away from Qining.

443
00:33:57,540 --> 00:33:59,600
So he was afraid that I would not come.

444
00:34:02,690 --> 00:34:03,300
He was not

445
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:04,300
good at speaking.

446
00:34:05,930 --> 00:34:07,060
He just looked at me.

447
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:11,030
The desire for a good helper in his eyes

448
00:34:13,409 --> 00:34:14,670
made me choose Qining.

449
00:34:26,580 --> 00:34:28,780
Among the two leaders who came that day,

450
00:34:29,659 --> 00:34:32,190
one died because he covered for his colleague

451
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:34,620
in the later operation,

452
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:38,940
the other was my old captain.

453
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:44,080
That day when we visited the graves,

454
00:34:44,530 --> 00:34:45,190
