463
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,730
The old captain's death

464
00:35:16,870 --> 00:35:18,400
was caused by these people.

465
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:22,920
So I always thought that

466
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:24,520
I dragged him down.

467
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:28,760
Later,

468
00:35:30,650 --> 00:35:32,650
