493
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:48,000
Wear it if you're not afraid of the cold.

494
00:37:02,550 --> 00:37:03,590
Can't we drive in?

495
00:37:05,270 --> 00:37:07,030
Grab a bite first.

496
00:37:07,650 --> 00:37:08,490
