530
00:39:29,970 --> 00:39:31,480
Hello, sister-in-law.

531
00:39:33,330 --> 00:39:34,410
Hello.

532
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:35,600
Let's eat.

533
00:39:38,210 --> 00:39:39,140
Let's eat first.

534
00:39:42,770 --> 00:39:43,430
Qin Mingyu.

535
00:39:43,790 --> 00:39:44,660
Serve some drinks.

536
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:45,110
Yes.

537
00:39:52,890 --> 00:39:54,350
