00:41:10,650 --> 00:41:11,710
Cooperate with me.

574
00:41:18,980 --> 00:41:19,780
How generous.

575
00:41:20,260 --> 00:41:21,570
This is my sister-in-law.

576
00:41:21,570 --> 00:41:22,100
Let's go.

577
00:41:22,810 --> 00:41:23,350
Take it.

578
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:38,100
Lean on me comfortably later.

579
00:41:38,530 --> 00:41:41,190
Five kilometres will take at least half an hour.

580
00:41:41,460 --> 00:41:42,420
If you don't feel well later,

581
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:43,050
just tell me.

582
00:41:43,050 --> 00:41:44,180
I'll change my pose.

583
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,330
How?

584
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,180
I'll do whatever you say.

585
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:50,100
Hold me tight.

586
00:42:05,700 --> 00:42:06,230
Who is it?

587
00:42:06,490 --> 00:42:08,370
Captain Lu, our former captain,

588
00:42:08,630 --> 00:42:10,520
brought his wife back to see his brothers.

589
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:12,050
Then he was taught a lesson.

590
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:13,340
Captain Lu runs fast.

591
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:15,690
How heavy are you now?

592
00:42:15,690 --> 00:42:16,420
Less than 90.

593
00:42:17,560 --> 00:42:18,900
You are underweight. Eat more.

594
00:42:18,900 --> 00:42:19,460
Go, Captain Lu!

595
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:20,100
If you cook well,

596
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:20,940
I'll eat more.

597
00:42:23,820 --> 00:42:25,020
Good job, Captain Lu.

598
00:42:25,680 --> 00:42:26,810
Come on, Captain Lu.

599
00:42:26,820 --> 00:42:29,110
Go! Go! Captain Lu!

600
00:42:30,020 --> 00:42:31,420
Can't you slow down a bit?

601
00:42:31,610 --> 00:42:33,470
They didn't set you a speed limit.

602
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:35,700
Twenty minutes to

603
00:42:35,700 --> 00:42:37,500
finish a five-kilometre run with a load

604
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:38,960
is the basic requirement.

605
00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:40,940
As the former captain,

606
00:42:41,110 --> 00:42:41,720
I can't disappoint.
